summary: This simply tells all NPC in College of Winterhold to not use archmage chamber while they go to/from Arcanaeum.
descriptionHtml:
This simply tells all NPC in College of Winterhold to not use archmage chamber while they go to/from Arcanaeum.
Made this mod for personal use as such NPC behavior was bothering me for a very long time and I found no mods that fix this. After some successful tests decided to share.
author: mluppov
